  49   1      
  50   1         //  Receiver enabled.
  51   1         //  8-bit data, 1 start bit, 1 stop bit, 
  52   1         //  Variable baud rate (asynchronous)
  53   1         //  Receive flag will only be set if a valid stop bit is received
  54   1         //  Set TI (transmit buffer is empty)
